skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: garage checker
des: This skill allows students to check how full the garages are at the University of Central Florida. Users can ask: how full is garage A, B, C, D, H, I, or Libra, how full are all garages, or what is the emptiest garage. This skill allows students to plan where they will park before driving around campus.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
